Package: dyprop
Type: Package
Title: Dynamic Proportionality Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("DyProp", "Team", email = "dev@dyprop.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: A high-performance statistical engine to identify the mechanism of 
    network rewiring in longitudinal genomic data (scRNA-seq, scDNA-seq, Multi-omics).
    Integrates Compositional Data Analysis (CoDa) with Singular Perturbation Theory 
    to detect stoichiometric switches and network decoupling.
